#import "/_lib/0.1.1.typ": *
#show: template

#taxon[Definition]
#title[Cauchy exponential species of types]

For a species $S: Uu_1 ->  Uu_2$ and we define the _cauchy exponential_ at $X : Uu_1$ as
$
  "exp"(S)(X) := Sigma_(U: Uu_1) Sigma_(V : U ->  Uu_1) Sigma_(e:(Sigma_(u:U) V(u)) ~= X) Pi_(u:U) S(V(u))
$
